title: United Kingdom Imports Intra Eu - Tanning, Dyeing Extracts, Other Colouring
description: Imports Intra Eu - Tanning, Dyeing Extracts, Other Colouring in the United Kingdom decreased to 116.13 GBP Million in September from 119.75 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports Intra Eu - Tanning, Dyeing Extracts, Other in the United Kingdom averaged 90.16 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 170.34 GBP Million in March of 2019 and a record low of 41.09 GBP Million in February of 2022.
